                    </div>
                    <h2 className="text-3xl font-black text-stone-200 font-serif mb-4 tracking-tight">The Forge lies in Ruins</h2>
                    <p className="text-stone-400 mb-10 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                        Your journey as a blacksmith starts with a single spark. To begin forging weapons and armor, you must first install a <span className="text-amber-500 font-bold">Furnace</span> from the market.
                    </p>
                    <div className="flex flex-col w-full gap-3">
                        <button 
                            onClick={() => onNavigate('MARKET')}
